<li id="cite_note-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.pbs.org/tesla/ll/images/ww_drawing02.gif" class="external text" title="http://www.pbs.org/tesla/ll/images/ww_drawing02.gif" rel="nofollow">pbs.org drawing (gif)</a></li>
